      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t以电工名义/职业申请澳洲独立移民PR应该有希望，澳洲社会对电工有需求，且电工职业在移民局的职业列表上。既然英文不错，可以自己搜寻一下，比如这网页：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly92aXNhLWdvLmNvbS8yMDIzLzAyLzEwL2VsZWN0cmljaWFuLW1vdmluZy10by1hdXN0cmFsaWEvIzp.OnRleHQ9RWxlY3RyaWNpYW5zJTIwYXJlJTIwaW4lMjBkZW1hbmQlMjBpbixhcHBseSUyMGZvciUyMGElMjB2aXNhJTIwZmlyc3Qu\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://visa-go.com/2023/02/10/electrician-moving-to-australia/#:~:text=Electricians%20are%20in%20demand%20in,apply%20for%20a%20visa%20first.\">https://visa-go.com/2023/02/10/electrician-moving-to-australia/#:~:text=Electricians%20are%20in%20demand%20in,apply%20for%20a%20visa%20first.</a>https://visa-go.com/2023/02/10/electrician-moving-to-australia/#:~:text=Electricians%20are%20in%20demand%20in,apply%20for%20a%20visa%20first.澳洲目前工党政府对移民较宽松。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-21",
